text: We have always relied on CA Casualty Auto and Home Insurance for the past 17-years and that is commitment. We appreciate the full attention their customer care agents provide for our family. Not once has there ever been a delay or any feeling of not wanting to help. We were always cared for--we love that! Thank you California Casualty Auto and Home Insurance!
